  "title": "HAIRSTYLIST",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Welcome customers and identify their preferences by asking pointed questions.</p>\n<p>• Recommend hairstyles and haircuts according to customers’ face shapes and tastes.</p>\n<p>• Cut, trim and shave hair using professional equipment.</p>\n<p>• Apply a wide range of hair coloring techniques, like highlights.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Possess good experience to the above.</p>\n<p>• Hands-on experience with various coloring techniques.</p>\n<p>• Knowledge of a wide range of haircuts, suitable for all hair lengths (e.g. braids and top knots).</p>\n<p>• Good interpersonal and communication skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
